{"tid":791013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵客攻略介紹「表哥」出場","createTime":"2018-08-23T12:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T14:16:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91e76786ebd0789125e407644c992904060fb1f1","tid":791013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180823/20482539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F20482539&d=8UZu4XPRPMtH7sbCkS5V%2Bp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a62642b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F20482539&h=b2c675e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180823/20482539</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月23日 <br />\n<br />\n搵客攻略介紹「表哥」出場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180823/large/23la2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180823%2Flarge%2F23la2p3.jpg&h=1c79b83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉案詐騙集團的「搵客攻略」詳列針對香港客戶的五部曲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方搗破倫敦金詐騙集團，撿獲大批證物包括講稿及劇本，由教職員透過交友App搵客，到投資公司副總裁的角色扮演，以及如何應付客人提問等，一應俱全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇本提醒勿貼異性合照<br />\n<br />\n警方撿獲的文件顯示詐騙集團主要透過交友App搵客，包括微信、花田、我在找你、Say Hi、遇見、陌陌、BeeTalk等。<br />\n<br />\n其中有針對香港客戶的五部曲，教導職員如何搵客，交友後首先如朋友般攀談；其後透過對話套取對方的個人資料，包括工作、住址、薪金及電話，繼而打開投資話題；之後令對方對投資感興趣；第四步是介紹「表哥」出場，指「表哥」是投資公司高層，所有投資都交給他協助賺錢；最後要與目標保持聯絡，定時展示「上表哥公司攞錢」的相片，不過強調不能貼出和異性合照，藉以取信目標客人。<br />\n<br />\n講稿筆記中又為「表哥」度身訂做副總裁的身份，教他吹噓「幫表妹投資賺錢」，日常忙於出差、打理酒莊、睇巿、操盤及見客等。當客人提出質疑：「點解要你做？」就要以謙卑真誠態度說服對方：「我未必比其他嘅人叻&hellip;&hellip;你24小時打畀我都可以幫你&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n扮低息貸款　 倫敦金「變臉」呃2,450萬　 講師中伏　警掃場拘15人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n受害人轟金管局卸責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受害人轟金管局卸責<br />\n<br />\n倫敦金騙案半年涉款8,100萬<br />\n<br />\n扮低息貸款　倫敦金「變臉」呃2,450萬　講師中伏　警掃場拘15人"},{"pid":"2bfab0b09fd2db8c12b799d85a961f4488f4f900","tid":791013,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"呢排又會突然做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係大家傾唔掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caed3a9749f02509e4c18d58a467f2c0b5f79335","tid":791013,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/205000_f357efb8aaa33953a089541e178b132c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F205000_f357efb8aaa33953a089541e178b132c.png&h=61da18a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89af80e043d37c20e1b9bcfabb2034c1927b7b12","tid":791013,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"老表你你好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898c30b583e2e50b87ea201ade4b958e2376ae64","tid":791013,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"立花BB?"}]}